LazyLibrarian is a program to follow authors and grab metadata for
all your digital reading needs.

It uses a combination of Librarything OpenLibrary and optionally
GoogleBooks as sources for author info and book info.
License: GNU GPL v3

LazyLibrarian used GoodReads extensively for author and book info,
but they have now shut down their api. If you have an existing
lazylibrarian installation you will need to move provider.

LazyLibrarian runs by default on port 5299 at http://localhost:5299
